H63-45 DATE: Aug, 63
CONTENTS: Williams. E.

57
00:03:28,478 --> 00:03:31,441
Last known address 
was this flophouse.

58
00:03:31,655 --> 00:03:34,408
Word on the street is 
our guy surfaces today.

59
00:03:34,408 --> 00:03:37,406
He's been wanted on 
this warrarnt for six months.

60
00:03:37,406 --> 00:03:38,800
