62
00:03:44,417 --> 00:03:46,292
Will?

63
00:03:47,881 --> 00:03:51,074
Hey. What is it?

64
00:03:51,333 --> 00:03:54,339
Body was found here, 
42 years ago.

65
00:03:54,339 --> 00:03:55,873
Whose body?

66
00:03:55,873 --> 00:03:57,660
Sixteen year old boy.

67
00:03:57,660 --> 00:03:59,164
Zeke Williams.

68
00:03:59,164 --> 00:04:00,371
Cold job?

69
00:04:00,371 --> 00:04:02,483
Never came in.

70
00:04:02,483 --> 00:04:05,932
Every year, 
folks would leave flowers.

71
00:04:06,057 --> 00:04:09,869
- Not this year.
- People forget.

72
00:04:11,903 --> 00:04:15,667
I was the one who found him, Lil.

73
00:04:19,528 --> 00:04:21,393
I never forgot.

